These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, chess, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, italian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the thai is the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is not the person playing monopoly##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the thai##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
7. the brazilian is somewhere between the person playing chess and the colombian##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person playing go and the person playing chess##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game   | chess   | canasta      | go   | monopoly  |
| Nationality   | thai    | italian   | brazilian | colombian  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

