4. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
8. the person playing scrabble is not the british##6

