.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, bus, airplane
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, musical, spy
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, lizard, rat
 1. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching spy movies##7
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Transport         | tram | jet-ski      | bus | airplane |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | martial-arts | horror  | spy       |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard       | fish    | hedgehog  |

