.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-9::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, broccoli, papaya
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, horror, superhero
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, havana, aristoff, davidoff
1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person eating asparagus##7
5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
6. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
7. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
9. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | blueberry  | broccoli  | asparagus | papaya   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | superhero | crime     | horror   |
| Cigar           | fonseca | havana       | aristoff      | davidoff |

