4. the fan of metal is on the right of the architect##1
5. the fan of punk is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
6. the nurse is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the nurse is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is sailing##7
8. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
