4. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
8. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who likes pink##6

.:: Answer ::.
